Used Extensions:
-> Brackets Color Picker        :: https://github.com/mikailcolak/brackets-color-picker
-> Brackets Css Color Preview   :: https://github.com/cmgddd/Brackets-css-color-preview
-> Brackets Icons               :: https://github.com/ivogabe/Brackets-Icons
-> Brackets Link File           :: https://github.com/pelatx/brackets-link-file
-> PHP SmartHints               :: https://github.com/Brackets-PHP/Brackets-PHP-SmartHints
-> QuickDocsPHP                 :: https://github.com/Wikunia/brackets-QuickDocsPHP
-> Todo                         :: https://github.com/mikaeljorhult/brackets-todo

Add to pref:
"highlightMatches": true